headline: Expedia price target raised to $185 from $180 at Morgan Stanley
summary: Morgan Stanley analyst Brian Nowak raised the firm’s price target on Expedia (EXPE) to $185 from $180 and keeps an Equal Weight rating on the shares. The firm sees GPU enabled and GenAI tool adoption driving fundamental upside and outperformance among the North American Internet group.
